r to metering tipcharts), gray air gap eductors for Comet w/Bleach and Comet DisinfectingCleaner with Bleach, hose barbs that connect the supply tubing to the Cometeductors, inlet water strainers, Select equipment knobs and suction inlet onall Select equipment. On the checklist, select all items from the list thatapply. If unable to replace any of these parts or if any of these parts hadalready been replaced during the current CY, please explain in Comments. Operational PM Requirements:  Operational PMs of the non-MWW PGP equipment includestesting and repairing the equipment as needed to ensure proper operation anddilution. Testing all sanitizer levels will be part of each Operational PM. Italso includes cleaning the equipment on every visit. If needed, the tech willreplace stickers, wall charts, and any parts required to keep the equipmentoperational.]]></POLICY>
