            <ITEM fqid="242159" is_admin_question="0" is_focus_question="0" is_info_only="0" qid="2009" question_code="016c" question_type="Select All That Apply" typeid="6">
                <QUESTION><![CDATA[3-Lever(s) CQ Quat Sanitizer Action Taken]]></QUESTION>
                <POLICY><![CDATA[After finishing work on the equipment choose as many of the pre-typed selections that apply. If the CQ Quat test does not reach 200 PPM, ensure that the result is within range of the US Health Department requirements of 150 PPM ? 400 PPM and note the final test result in the comment. Describe in the comment any suspected root causes preventing a test result of 200 PPM.]]></POLICY>
