            <ITEM fqid="242187" is_admin_question="0" is_focus_question="0" is_info_only="0" qid="1512" question_code="028z" question_type="Select All That Apply" typeid="6">
                <QUESTION><![CDATA[Training completed with the personnel on this visit]]></QUESTION>
                <POLICY><![CDATA[As the FST progresses through the PM or RE visit, he/she may observe opportunities for training store employees on the P&G program. The FST should provide brief training based on these observations. Also, employees may ask questions about the cleaning procedures, P&G products, P&G equipment, etc. The FST should be prepared to answer those questions. With some customers, specific training topics may be provided to the FST for training on each visit. Please indicate the type of training provided by selecting from the multiselect picklist. Select all training topics from the list for which you provided training. Also provide brief details of the training conducted in the Comments box. Documenting the Titles and/or Names of persons trained in the Comment box is required. Selections that are followed with 'COMMENT' require details in the Comment box. You may also provide details for other selections as appropriate. If no training was done, provide a comment explaining why no training was done.]]></POLICY>
