            <ITEM fqid="242156" is_admin_question="0" is_focus_question="0" is_info_only="0" qid="1797" question_code="023k" question_type="Data Capture" typeid="3">
                <QUESTION><![CDATA[What was the Wash Cycle-Wash Pressure?]]></QUESTION>
                <POLICY><![CDATA[If the rack washer is operating check the water pressure gauge and record the water pressure of the final rinse cycle. It should be between 15 PSI & 25 PSI with 20 PSI the optimum. If the rack washer in not operating and you can run a short cycle record the final rinse water pressure. If the final rinse pressure is outside the 15 ? 25 PSI range notify the PIC.]]></POLICY>
